Use the titanic data set

Source: R/use-data.R
use_data_titanic.Rd

This data set comes with base R. Survival of passengers on the Titanic.

Usage

use_data_titanic(count = FALSE)

Arguments

count

use count data

Value

Dataset

Examples

use_data_titanic(count = TRUE)
#> # A tibble: 32 × 5
#>    Class Sex    Age   Survived     n
